title: Phish - 2013-07-13 Columbia, MD
description:
Saturday, 07/13/2013 
Merriweather Post Pavillion, Columbia, MD

Soundcheck: Yarmouth Road, Energy, Architect, Jam

Set 1: Kill Devil Falls, Destiny Unbound, Taste, Halfway to the Moon, Twenty Years Later, Maze, Yarmouth Road, Split Open and Melt

Set 2: Down with Disease > Free > Bouncing Around the Room, Birds of a Feather, Harry Hood[1] > Architect > Mike's Song > Simple > Weekapaug Groove

Encore: Waste > Good Times Bad Times

[1] BOAF and Divided Sky teases by Trey; Dog Log tease by Mike.

Performers: Trey Anastasio, Page McConnell, Jon Fishman, Mike Gordon

Notes: Hood featured a BOAF and Divided Sky teases by Trey and a Dog Log tease by Mike.
